<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>OpinionHub - People's Opinion Platform</title>

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:'Segoe UI',sans-serif;
}

body{

background:
linear-gradient(
rgba(0,0,0,.65),
rgba(0,0,0,.65)
),

url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552664730-d307ca884978?w=1800");

background-size:cover;
background-position:center;
background-attachment:fixed;

color:white;
}

/* NAVBAR */

nav{

display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;

padding:20px 60px;

background:rgba(0,0,0,.25);

backdrop-filter:blur(12px);

position:sticky;
top:0;
}

.logo{

font-size:34px;
font-weight:bold;

color:#00E5FF;
}

nav ul{

display:flex;
gap:30px;

list-style:none;
}

nav ul li{

cursor:pointer;
transition:.3s;
}

nav ul li:hover{

color:#00E5FF;
}

.btn{

padding:12px 25px;

border:none;

border-radius:30px;

font-weight:bold;

cursor:pointer;

background:
linear-gradient(
45deg,
#00E5FF,
#4FC3F7
);

color:black;
}

/* HERO */

.hero{

height:90vh;

display:flex;
flex-direction:column;

justify-content:center;
align-items:center;

text-align:center;

padding:20px;
}

.hero h1{

font-size:80px;

margin-bottom:20px;

background:
linear-gradient(
90deg,
#ffffff,
#00E5FF,
#ffffff
);

-webkit-background-clip:text;
-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
}

.hero p{

font-size:22px;

max-width:900px;

color:#dffbff;
}

/* POLL BOX */

.poll-box{

margin-top:35px;

background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);

backdrop-filter:blur(12px);

padding:30px;

border-radius:20px;

width:650px;
}

.poll-box h2{

margin-bottom:20px;

color:#00E5FF;
}

.poll-box label{

display:block;

margin:12px 0;
}

.poll-box textarea{

width:100%;

padding:12px;

border:none;

border-radius:10px;

margin-top:15px;
}

/* STATS */

.stats{

display:flex;

justify-content:center;

flex-wrap:wrap;

gap:25px;

padding:50px;
}

.stat-card{

width:220px;

padding:25px;

text-align:center;

background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);

backdrop-filter:blur(10px);

border-radius:20px;
}

.stat-card h2{

color:#00E5FF;
}

/* SECTION TITLE */

.section-title{

text-align:center;

font-size:40px;

color:#00E5FF;

margin:50px 0;
}

/* OPINION CARDS */

.container{

display:flex;

justify-content:center;

flex-wrap:wrap;

gap:30px;

padding:20px 40px 60px;
}

.card{

width:320px;

padding:25px;

background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);

backdrop-filter:blur(15px);

border-radius:20px;

transition:.4s;
}

.card:hover{

transform:translateY(-10px);

box-shadow:
0 15px 35px rgba(0,229,255,.3);
}

.card h3{

color:#00E5FF;

margin-bottom:10px;
}

/* FOOTER */

footer{

text-align:center;

padding:25px;

background:rgba(0,0,0,.4);
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<nav>

<div class="logo">📊 OpinionHub</div>

<ul>

<li>Home</li>
<li>Polls</li>
<li>Opinions</li>
<li>Results</li>
<li>Contact</li>

</ul>

<button class="btn">Login</button>

</nav>

<section class="hero">

<h1>Your Opinion Matters</h1>

<p>

Share your views, participate in surveys,
and discover what people think about important topics.

</p>

<div class="poll-box">

<h2>Current Survey</h2>

<p>
What is the most important factor in choosing a smartphone?
</p>

<label>
<input type="radio" name="poll">
Price
</label>

<label>
<input type="radio" name="poll">
Camera Quality
</label>

<label>
<input type="radio" name="poll">
Battery Life
</label>

<label>
<input type="radio" name="poll">
Performance
</label>

<textarea rows="4"
placeholder="Share your opinion...">
</textarea>

<br><br>

<button class="btn">

Submit Opinion

</button>

</div>

</section>

<div class="stats">

<div class="stat-card">
<h2>50K+</h2>
<p>Opinions Collected</p>
</div>

<div class="stat-card">
<h2>1000+</h2>
<p>Active Surveys</p>
</div>

<div class="stat-card">
<h2>25K+</h2>
<p>Registered Users</p>
</div>

<div class="stat-card">
<h2>98%</h2>
<p>Participation Rate</p>
</div>

</div>

<h2 class="section-title">

Popular Opinion Categories

</h2>

<div class="container">

<div class="card">

<h3>📱 Technology</h3>

<p>
Share opinions on gadgets, AI, software and emerging technologies.
</p>

</div>

<div class="card">

<h3>🎓 Education</h3>

<p>
Discuss learning methods, universities and online education.
</p>

</div>

<div class="card">

<h3>🌍 Environment</h3>

<p>
Express views on sustainability and environmental issues.
</p>

</div>

<div class="card">

<h3>⚽ Sports</h3>

<p>
Vote and share opinions on teams, tournaments and players.
</p>

</div>

</div>

<footer>

📊 OpinionHub - Web Service for Finding People's Opinion © 2026

</footer>

</body>

</html>
